						<li id="comment-8270" class="comment c25 c-y2010 c-m02 c-d24 c-h01">
							<div class="comment-author vcard"> <span class="fn n"><a href='http://blog.evanweaver.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url url'>evan</a></span></div>
